	   <tr><td colspan=2>Affliction efficiency 4 is currently bugged and only operates on spells below level 60, not level 65. If you have one, please feedback/bug it.<br><br>Note that it does not only modify HP spells - it also works on afflictions in general, so debuffs/dots/mezzes are also cheaper.<br><br>And yes, I know it's a necro item and I'm an enc. I use the Sharp Claw Ahlspiess, which has the same focus effect, and that's the bugged part.<br><br>Lath, Coercer, Veeshan.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Nov 11 00:58:26 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
